---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="How It Works | Releaf MD" 
  description="Learn how the Florida medical marijuana card certification process works. Step-by-step guidance for new patients, transfers, renewals, seniors, and children."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-brand-mint py-16 lg:py-24 border-b border-brand-primary/10 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(#1D8C64_1px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:16px_16px] opacity-10"></div>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center space-y-4 relative z-10">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 bg-brand-primary/10 text-brand-primary rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
        📋 Step-By-Step Process
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark leading-tight uppercase font-black">How It Works</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Simple, secure, and fully guided pathways to certified relief under Florida regulations.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Visitor Paths Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark uppercase">Select Your Pathway</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-2">We tailor the certification process based on your specific needs. Choose your path below:</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Path 1: New Patient -->
        <div class="bg-brand-mint/40 border border-brand-primary/10 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-whisper hover-lift flex flex-col justify-between">
          <div>
            <span class="text-3xl">🌱</span>
            <h3 class="font-serif-headline font-bold text-brand-dark text-lg uppercase mt-3 mb-2">New Patients</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-xs leading-relaxed mb-4">
              If you have never had a Florida medical marijuana card before, state law requires an in-person physical assessment. We will walk you through qualifying conditions, verify your records, and register you in the OMMU registry.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <a href="/evaluations" class="block text-center bg-brand-primary hover:bg-brand-dark text-white text-xs font-bold py-2.5 rounded-full transition-colors">
              New Patient Guide
            </a>
            <a href="https://live.vcita.com/site/DrKellyKing/online-scheduling?service=xnfeicu6jent0179" class="block text-center border border-brand-primary/20 text-brand-primary text-xs font-bold py-2.5 rounded-full hover:bg-brand-mint transition-colors">
              Book Initial Exam
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Path 2: Renewals -->
        <div class="bg-brand-mint/40 border border-brand-primary/10 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-whisper hover-lift flex flex-col justify-between">
          <div>
            <span class="text-3xl">🔄</span>
            <h3 class="font-serif-headline font-bold text-brand-dark text-lg uppercase mt-3 mb-2">Renewals & Follow-ups</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-xs leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Florida recommendations expire every 30 weeks (210 days). For established patients, our follow-up consultations can be completed quickly via secure telehealth or in-person to prevent dispensary access lapses.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <a href="/renewals" class="block text-center bg-brand-accent hover:bg-brand-dark text-white text-xs font-bold py-2.5 rounded-full transition-colors">
              Renewal Details
            </a>
            <a href="https://live.vcita.com/site/DrKellyKing/online-scheduling?service=fo0js3iwqegdlams" class="block text-center border border-brand-accent/20 text-brand-accent text-xs font-bold py-2.5 rounded-full hover:bg-brand-mint transition-colors">
              Book Renewal Now
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Path 3: Transfers -->
        <div class="bg-brand-mint/40 border border-brand-primary/10 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-whisper hover-lift flex flex-col justify-between">
          <div>
            <span class="text-3xl">🤝</span>
            <h3 class="font-serif-headline font-bold text-brand-dark text-lg uppercase mt-3 mb-2">Doctor Transfers</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-xs leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Switching your certifying physician to Releaf MD is completely seamless. We coordinate the transition in the state registry to cancel your old orders and activate new ones without duplicate state fees.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <a href="/evaluations" class="block text-center bg-brand-dark hover:bg-brand-primary text-white text-xs font-bold py-2.5 rounded-full transition-colors">
              Transfer Process
            </a>
            <a href="https://live.vcita.com/site/DrKellyKing/online-scheduling?service=fo0js3iwqegdlams" class="block text-center border border-brand-dark/20 text-brand-dark text-xs font-bold py-2.5 rounded-full hover:bg-brand-mint transition-colors">
              Transfer To Us
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process Timeline Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-brand-mint/20 border-t border-b border-brand-primary/10">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark uppercase">The 4-Step Journey</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-2">What you can expect from start to finish.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 relative">
        <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-6 left-6 right-6 h-0.5 bg-brand-primary/20 z-0"></div>

        <div class="relative z-10 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-brand-primary/10 text-center hover-lift">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg mx-auto mb-4 shadow-sm">1</div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-sm uppercase">1. Schedule</h4>
          <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 mt-2 leading-relaxed">Book online or call us. We confirm eligibility and prepare your clinical intake forms.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="relative z-10 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-brand-primary/10 text-center hover-lift">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg mx-auto mb-4 shadow-sm">2</div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-sm uppercase">2. Consult</h4>
          <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 mt-2 leading-relaxed">Meet Dr. Kelly Ennix King for a compassionate, individualized evaluation of your medical needs.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="relative z-10 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-brand-primary/10 text-center hover-lift">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-accent text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg mx-auto mb-4 shadow-sm">3</div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-sm uppercase">3. Registry</h4>
          <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 mt-2 leading-relaxed">Our clinic inputs your certification details directly into the Florida Medical Marijuana Use Registry.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="relative z-10 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-brand-primary/10 text-center hover-lift">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-accent text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg mx-auto mb-4 shadow-sm">4</div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-sm uppercase">4. Purchase</h4>
          <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 mt-2 leading-relaxed">Once the state approves your fee payment, buy instantly at any licensed dispensary using your digital ID.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Specialized Resources Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-12">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark uppercase">Specialized Care & Wellness Programs</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-2">We provide tailored guides for specific demographics and innovative wellness therapies.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Seniors -->
        <div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-250 p-6 rounded-2xl text-center flex flex-col justify-between hover-lift">
          <div>
            <span class="text-2xl block mb-2">👵</span>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-sm uppercase">Senior Resources</h4>
            <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 mt-2 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Tailored guidance focusing on non-smokable alternatives, safe dosing, and drug interaction reviews.
            </p>
          </div>
          <a href="/seniors" class="text-xs font-bold text-brand-accent hover:underline">Seniors Guide &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Pediatric -->
        <div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-250 p-6 rounded-2xl text-center flex flex-col justify-between hover-lift">
          <div>
            <span class="text-2xl block mb-2">🧸</span>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-sm uppercase">Pediatric CBD</h4>
            <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 mt-2 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Clinical support for parents seeking two-physician approvals and legal caregiver registration for minors.
            </p>
          </div>
          <a href="/pediatric-cbd" class="text-xs font-bold text-brand-accent hover:underline">Pediatric Guide &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <!-- IV CBD -->
        <div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-250 p-6 rounded-2xl text-center flex flex-col justify-between hover-lift">
          <div>
            <span class="text-2xl block mb-2">💧</span>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-sm uppercase">IV CBD Infusions</h4>
            <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 mt-2 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Advanced PICO IV CBD & NAD+ therapy delivering 100% absorption for total body homeostasis and ECS support.
            </p>
          </div>
          <a href="/cbd-iv-infusions" class="text-xs font-bold text-brand-accent hover:underline">IV CBD Details &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
